snippet.title: Power Rangers Samurai - Wii / DS - Become a Samurai Rangers
snippet.description:
Based on Saban Brands' incredibly popular Power Rangers Samurai, players of all ages will finally be able to join the Rangers as they physically immerse themselves into the morphing action of the iconic team of heroes.

Power Rangers Samurai will be available this year.
For more information, please visit your local Namco Bandai Games website: http://www.namcobandaigames.eu
